    'Identify situations that might make change harder; Create flexible coping responses; Normalize setbacks and focus on learning; Separate behavior from identity',
    'A colleague has started in a new role and is preparing for challenges. Practice helping them anticipate difficulties and plan for setbacks.',
    '{"name": "Priya", "role": "colleague", "background": "Recently promoted to Team Lead. Enthusiastic but aware of challenges ahead. Wants to maintain success.", "personality_traits": ["motivated", "self-aware", "cautious", "reflective"], "tone_spectrum": {"word_complexity": 0.4, "sentence_length": 0.4, "emotional_expressiveness": 0.4, "disclosure_level": 0.4, "response_latency": 0.4, "confidence_level": 0.4}, "starting_tone_position": 0.4, "triggers": ["pressure", "dismissiveness", "unrealistic expectations"], "comfort_topics": ["support", "learning", "growth", "realism"]}'::jsonb,
    '{"start_node_id": "anti_1", "nodes": {"anti_1": {"id": "anti_1", "persona_text": "I''ve been in the Team Lead role for a few weeks now and it''s going well. I feel good about my progress.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_1_0", "option_text": "That''s great! Just make sure you keep it up. You have to maintain this level of performance.", "preview_hint": "Pressure approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This creates pressure without actually preparing for challenges.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_1_1", "option_text": "That''s really wonderful progress. As you continue, what situations might make it harder to maintain this momentum?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "anticipatory_coping"], "competency_links": ["A6", "B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - affirms success and proactively prepares for challenges without being pessimistic.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2b", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_1_2", "option_text": "Be careful. Most new leads struggle after the first month.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This emphasizes failure rather than building preparation skills.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_2a": {"id": "anti_2a", "persona_text": "Oh, now I''m worried. Maybe I was being too optimistic.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_2a_0", "option_text": "I didn''t mean to worry you. Your success so far shows you''re capable. What I meant was, what challenges do you think might come up?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good recovery - affirms capability and reframes to constructive problem-solving.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2b", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_2a_1", "option_text": "You should be worried. Most new leads struggle after month one.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This reinforces discouragement rather than building coping skills.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_2b": {"id": "anti_2b", "persona_text": "Well, we have some complex cases coming up. And performance reviews are next month - I''ll be doing those for the first time. There might be some difficult conversations there.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Barriers"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_2b_0", "option_text": "You can''t let those be excuses. You need to prioritize your leadership responsibilities.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This labels legitimate challenges as ''excuses'' rather than problem-solving.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_2b_1", "option_text": "Complex cases and first-time performance reviews - those are real challenges many new leads face. What has helped you handle difficult situations in the past?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["validation", "resource_elicitation"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent - normalizes challenges and explores colleague''s existing coping resources.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_3a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_2b_2", "option_text": "Don''t worry about it. Just do your best.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This minimizes the challenge without collaboratively problem-solving.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_3a": {"id": "anti_3a", "persona_text": "In the past, I''ve found that preparing really helps. For difficult customer conversations, I would think through my approach beforehand. And asking for advice when I was stuck - that''s helped me too.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_3a_0", "option_text": "So preparation and seeking support are strategies that have worked for you before. For these upcoming challenges, what might preparation look like?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "planning"], "competency_links": ["A6", "B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - reinforces existing coping and creates implementation intention for the challenge.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_4a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_3a_1", "option_text": "You need to do more than prepare. You need to execute perfectly.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This creates unrealistic pressure and doesn''t acknowledge that flexibility might be needed.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_4a": {"id": "anti_4a", "persona_text": "For the performance reviews, I could prepare by reviewing each person''s file beforehand, and maybe talk to another lead about their approach. For the complex cases, I could bring in more experienced colleagues for consultation.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_4a_0", "option_text": "Those are smart, proactive strategies - preparing thoroughly and seeking expert consultation when needed. How would you feel about yourself if, despite all this preparation, something didn''t go as planned?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "setback_normalization"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent - reinforces the adaptive plan and proactively addresses potential self-judgment.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_5a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_4a_1", "option_text": "Those are good plans. You need to stick to them perfectly.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This creates unrealistic expectations about flawless execution.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_5a": {"id": "anti_5a", "persona_text": "Honestly? I''d probably feel like I failed. That I''m not cut out for leadership if I can''t handle it perfectly.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_5a_0", "option_text": "If things don''t go perfectly, you''ve failed. That''s just the reality of leadership.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This reinforces unhelpful all-or-nothing thinking about setbacks.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_5a_1", "option_text": "Setbacks are a common part of any new role, not failure. Something not going perfectly doesn''t mean you''re not capable. What would you tell a team member who was being hard on themselves after a mistake?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["normalization", "perspective"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - normalizes setbacks and uses perspective to challenge self-judgment.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_6a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_6a": {"id": "anti_6a", "persona_text": "I''d tell them that everyone makes mistakes, especially in a new role. I''d say the important thing is to learn from it and keep going. I guess I''m harder on myself than I''d be on them.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Barriers"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_6a_0", "option_text": "You''d be compassionate with a team member. What would it be like to extend that same kindness to yourself if things don''t go perfectly?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["reflection", "self_compassion"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good - highlights the insight and invites applying it to self.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_7a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_6a_1", "option_text": "Well, you should be hard on yourself. That''s what creates excellence.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This contradicts the helpful insight they just had.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_7a": {"id": "anti_7a", "persona_text": "That would be... different. I think it would help me recover faster instead of spiraling into self-doubt. Maybe I''d be more willing to try again instead of giving up.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_anti_7a_0", "option_text": "So if you do have a setback during these performance reviews or with a complex case, what might help you recover and keep going?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["planning", "coping"], "competency_links": ["B1"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - creates a specific plan for recovery from setback.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_good", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_anti_7a_1", "option_text": "Good, but try not to have setbacks. Just do everything right.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This undoes the helpful work on normalizing and planning for setbacks.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "anti_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "anti_end_good": {"id": "anti_end_good", "persona_text": "I think reminding myself that mistakes are part of learning would help. And reaching out for support instead of isolating myself. Also, focusing on what went well, not just what didn''t. That balanced approach would keep me moving forward.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Identity"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "neutral_end"}, "anti_end_poor": {"id": "anti_end_poor", "persona_text": "I feel like if I make a mistake, I''ll have failed. This conversation has actually made me more nervous about the challenges ahead.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "failed_engagement"}}}'::jsonb,
